            Yes, we connect expats with relocation services throughout Switzerland, covering all 26 cantons and major cities. Our network includes specialists in every region from Zurich to Geneva, Basel to Bern.
            </p>
          </div>
          
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
